      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior paint and body are flawless, with no scratches, dents, or imperfections. The interior is in pristine state, showing no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs as new with all systems functioning perfectly.",
      "price": 46000.0,
